<ul>
	<li>Mixed sprouts</li>
	<li>Spring onion with greens</li>
	<li>Parsley sprigs</li>
	<li>Coriander sprigs</li>
	<li>Finely chopped garlic</li>
	<li>Bread crumbs</li>
	<li>Seasonings (Salt, cumin powder, black pepper powder, red chilli powder)</li>
	<li>Baking soda</li>
	<li>Choice of oil for frying</li>
