<p>These simple signs will surely help you get the answer to, &ldquo;How can you tell if your ex still likes you?&rdquo; Since it is impossible to find out the truth and their genuine feelings, it is wise to have patience. The more you dive deeper, the more confusing the situation may seem. Hence, do not overanalyze their behavior. Any kind of strong emotion from your ex-partner is a signal that they still have feelings for you.&nbsp;</p>

<p>Alternatively, your ex might show negative emotions due to jealousy, anger, or sudden breakup. So, do not complicate things, take your time to analyze the situation, and communicate clearly and honestly.</p>
