<p>Now, that you have found all the reasons, refrain from asking, &ldquo;Why is my ex texting me?&rdquo; Instead, analyze the situation, try to resolve issues if any, respond with a sense of concern, or simply out of humanity. There are no hard or fast rules to get back or to ignore his or her messages. Every relationship is unique and every couple&rsquo;s way of dealing with things and issues differs.</p>
