]]></description><link>https://www.pinkvilla.com/lifestyle/relationships/10-year-anniversary-quotes-1357024</link><guid  isPermaLink="false">pinkvilla-1357024</guid><pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 15:52:09 +05:30</pubDate></item><item><title><![CDATA[How to Know If She Is the One: Signs She’s Your True Love]]></title><description><![CDATA[<img src="https://www.pinkvilla.com/images/2024-11/335156814_select-2024-10-30t151701-736.jpg"></img><p style="text-align:justify">Your loved ones are seriously your toughest critics! After all, they are the ones who genuinely want you to succeed, even if that means not sugarcoating words and telling you how to do things better for your own future. Life is long and most people don&rsquo;t want to be stuck with a partner that doesn&rsquo;t know how to provide encouragement and motivation.&nbsp;</p>

<p>So if you have found yourself a woman who criticizes you constructively for your own good and always urges you to hone your skills and make improvements, stick to her and understand that she&rsquo;s doing all this out of love and is the one for you!</p>

<h3><strong>16. You Feel Comfortable in Each Other&rsquo;s Presence&nbsp;</strong></h3>

<p>There is some warmth and serenity when spending time with our special one &mdash; even if there is complete silence, the happiness you get in each other&rsquo;s arms can&rsquo;t be compared to any of the world&rsquo;s luxuries. We all want comfort in life, especially when we want to settle down in a relationship!&nbsp;</p>

<p>Being able to be truly yourself, not hiding your quirks, being the goofball you are, and feeling comfortable around the person you love is a wish we all have. So if you feel that comfort around your partner, this is a clear sign that you both are meant for each other.&nbsp;</p>

<h3><strong>17. You Imagine Her in the Future</strong></h3>

<p>Do you always envision her in your future? Say you&rsquo;re planning to buy a house or a car &mdash; if at the back of your mind, you always think about her likes and dislikes, it means that the love is stored. Plus, if she too feels the same, it means you both desire to be in a committed relationship.</p>

<h3><strong>18. You Love Each Other</strong></h3>

<p>This one is a no-brainer &mdash; if there&rsquo;s mutual respect between the both of you and you love each other, she is the one for you and you are the one for her!</p>

<p style="text-align:justify">Sometimes, in love, our minds stop working &mdash; we are so much in love that we tend to look past our beloved&rsquo;s flaws and other things that could potentially harm the relationship. At other times, we are also confused and don&rsquo;t understand if the other person thinks love is as much as we love them.&nbsp;</p>

<p>Our detailed guide on how to know if she is the one can help you answer many questions concerning your relationship and take the next step. Remember that not all the parameters will be checked by your significant other &mdash; but if she ticks most of the boxes and you are sure that you both are meant for each other, you can take your relationship to the next level!</p>
